nodes.text: Star Wars Weekly 61 is the sixty-first issue in the Marvel Star Wars UK series of comics.

This issue includes the first of three parts of a story printed in the US as Star Wars 27. This is the first issue to start printing US stories in three parts instead of two, making room in the book for more pages than usual from the other non-Star Wars Marvel Comics stories already appearing in big number inside of it since Star Wars Weekly 2.
